	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If the music engine has potential to write to NES' 2A03 registers, you could re-route the FDS channel so that it's threated as a 2A03 squarewave channel, and place the output on one of the two MMC5 channel which is almost identical, but lacks sweeping.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
